Detailed Description

cvmx_pki_pcam_result

For diagnostic use only, this register returns PCAM results for the most recent write to PKI_PCAM_LOOKUP. The read will stall until the lookup is completed. PKI_CL()_ECC_CTL[PCAM_EN] must be clear before accessing this register. Read stall is implemented by delaying the PKI_PCAM_LOOKUP write acknowledge until the PCAM is free and the lookup can be issued.
